      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i get that it's complex, but from an economic standpoint, isn't it basically settled that tariffs are bad because they mess with free trade and raise prices? like, isn't the \"protection\" part just a myth that ignores the bigger picture of how much more people have to pay for everything?",
